      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Ideal as a budget commuter, first project, or something to tinker with on the weekends. If you\u2019re after a straightforward car at a sensible price and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and definitely worth a look.",
